dct_title_s: Spain 1:10,000. Reus city plan. A.M.S. M981
dct_description_sm: Map shows military and coast guard headquarters. Some streets and buildings are named. "Prepared from Spanish map 1:50,000, 472; Europe B24 - MG - 33. "Army Map Service, U. S. Army, Washington, D. C. 114984. 1943. 3-43." Military grid. AMS 1. Alternate title: Reus city plan. With key to street names. Projection approximate. Prepared from Spanish map 1:50,000 472; Europe B24-MG-33.
dct_publisher_sm: Washington, D.C. : Army Map Service, U.S. Army, 1943.
